        Social Proof for Weight Loss Coaches
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Someone considering a weight loss coach has tried things before. They've failed before. They're skeptical. The only thing that breaks through that skepticism is seeing that someone just like them succeeded with your program. Your testimonials are your most powerful sales tool — full stop.
